The 2H2O enrichment of the duplicate saliva samples was analyzed using Fourier Transform Infrared Spectroscopy at St. John's Research Institute in Bangalore, India. The 2H2O concentration of the baseline predose saliva sample was subtracted from the postdose saliva sample that had the highest 2H2O concentration. Total body water (TBW) was calculated using the following equation:
